1.5
log
@replace all references to bn(3) with BN_new(3),
and make sure all BN*(3) pages point back to BN_new(3)
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: BN_set_bit.3,v 1.4 2016/11/20 18:11:40 schwarze Exp $
.\"	OpenSSL b97fdb57 Nov 11 09:33:09 2016 +0100
.\"
